platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Make a routine & put on a show
ダンスムーブを披露しよう
Monte sur scène avec ta choré

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Bursting with beats and energy, Toca Dance will make the whole family want to get up and groove. This incredibly cute game puts kids in charge of their own musical production—choosing dancers, costumes, and techno tracks, and choreographing moves using simple swipes and taps. Once the performance starts, the real fun begins: you can fling items at the stage, set off pyrotechnics and other cool effects, and even cheer (or boo) your squad. Seeing the payoff—an awesome video you can share—will encourage players to jump right back in and start working on their next great show.
